edu.jhu.hlt.concrete.communications

Class SuperCommunication

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.jhu.hlt.concrete.communications.SuperCommunication
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConcreteEntityized, ConcreteEntityMentionized, ConcreteSectioned, ConcreteSentenced, ConcreteSituationized, ConcreteSituationMentionized, ConcreteTokenized
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SectionedSuperCommunication

    public class SuperCommunication
extends Object
implements ConcreteSituationized, ConcreteEntityized
    Read-only wrapper around Communication to allow advanced functionality.

    Be aware that changes to wrapped Communication objects are not propagated through to the SuperCommunication object.
    Author:
    max
